# Honda Sales Tablet

An AngularJS application powered by .NET WebAPI & MVC on the backend.

### Client Configuration

1. Install [Node.js](http://nodejs.org/) with NPM
2. Install [Git](https://code.google.com/p/msysgit/downloads/list?q=full+installer+official+git) and make sure it is available from your PATH
3. Install [Grunt](http://gruntjs.com/) globally from the command line: `npm install -g grunt-cli`
4. Install [Bower](http://bower.io/) globally from the command line: `npm install -g bower`
5. Run `npm install` in root folder (where package.json is located) to install the required server packages
6. Run `bower install` in the same folder to install required client packages (jQuery, Angular, etc.)

### Building

`grunt build`

- Minifies all JS, CSS & image files 
- Copies them to the `dist/` folder for the application to access.

### Running Client Tests

`grunt test`

